<includeonly><div class="kcRailBox" style="float:{{{float|right}}}">
<div class="kcRailTitle"><p>{{{title|}}}</p></div>
<div class="kcRailContent">
<div class="twitter-timeline-wrapper" data-width="{{{width|300}}}" data-height="{{{height|400}}}" data-profile="{{{profile|}}}" data-text="{{{text|}}}"></div>
</div>
</div></includeonly><noinclude>
==Usage==
<pre>
{{TwitterTimeline|profile=KanColle_STAFF|title=Official Staff Tweets|text=Tweets by KanColle_STAFF}}
{{TwitterTimeline|profile=dmmolg_com|title=Official DMM Tweets|text=Tweets by dmmolg_com}}
{{TwitterTimeline|profile=Kensho_KanColle|title=Kensho KanColle Tweets|text=Tweets by Kensho_KanColle}}
</pre>
Result:
{{TwitterTimeline|profile=KanColle_STAFF|title=Official Staff Tweets|text=Tweets by KanColle_STAFF}}
{{TwitterTimeline|profile=dmmolg_com|title=Official DMM Tweets|text=Tweets by dmmolg_com}}
{{TwitterTimeline|profile=Kensho_KanColle|title=Kensho KanColle Tweets|text=Tweets by Kensho_KanColle}}
{{clear}}
==Parameters==
* '''profile''': twitter profile name
* '''title''': <code>kcRailBox</code> title
* '''text''': text for widget header
* '''width''', '''height''': widget width and height, defaults to <code>300</code> and <code>400</code>
* '''float''': [http://www.w3schools.com/cssref/pr_class_float.asp float property], defaults to <code>right</code>
